gmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"244f75fa702408d5e9b17f8917030977e184378c","tid":1788401,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T14:51:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">SEASON'S GREETINGS <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"6782e9f3caae647d4d304029558f4854f7c655d9","tid":1788401,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T15:57:15.000Z","msg":"Yuletide Greetings"},{"pid":"2d745ff4bfb650e69aeb9cb34134f9338b8cb293","tid":1788401,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T16:19:57.000Z","msg":"Wishing you a holiday season full of warmth, love and family!"},{"pid":"8394c0eba93def9201f667c44a17234175aeafe2","tid":1788401,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T02:25:41.000Z","msg":"Wishing you a season full of Yuletide cheer!"},{"pid":"c742599b870f74ec896e97f5df32484030dca0d0","tid":1788401,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T15:28:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><ins>兔子在大自然的階級觀念</ins></span></span><br />\n<br />\n在大自然內，兔子有等級制度。一個高級(dominant)的兔子會groom (舔/梳理) 一個次級(inferior)兔子，但高級的亦會要求次級的兔子groom牠。當兔子低頭向前躺在地上，牠是想你groom (撫摸/親吻) 牠，這樣可以增加牠的自尊心、安全感、令牠舒適快樂。當牠們受驚時，也需要groom牠們，令到冷靜下來和知道是沒事的。兔子會騎着另一隻兔背後來顯示牠是較高層次(show dominance), 此行為停了就代表牠們已決定了等級制度。此行為是正常，無論兩隻是同性或異性。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">在0:59 可看到：</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Nyv4VhuZv_s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FNyv4VhuZv_s&d=CSzjam5d59%2B0TSQi2Kgm6kwFe44qEnauMGuWilFD6Zg%3D&h=3f9f384a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Nyv4VhuZv_s</a><br />\n<br />\n如果你在兔子面前<span style=\"color: gold;\">打開手掌</span>，對於牠來說是要求牠groom 你。如果你們關係好，牠會做。如果牠對主人感到憤怒，對於牠來說是不尊重牠，牠可能會用屁股對着你(代表生悶氣) 或嚴重的話，撲過來咬你。 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">主人要求兔仔groom 主人：</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/6DKeKyzZ67Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F6DKeKyzZ67Y&d=CSzjam5d59%2B0TSQi2Kgm6kwFe44qEnauMGuWilFD6Zg%3D&h=7d7d8867\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/6DKeKyzZ67Y</a><br />\n<br />\n以下兩隻兔子決定等級制度時<span style=\"color: gold;\">遇到困難</span>。一隻 groom另一隻, 但等了很久還未得到回報，所以發脾氣在<strong><em>2:08</em></strong>咬牠。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/af7_mGuD5Qg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Faf7_mGuD5Qg&d=CSzjam5d59%2B0TSQi2Kgm6kwFe44qEnauMGuWilFD6Zg%3D&h=16d7b2f9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/af7_mGuD5Qg</a><br />\n<br />\n除了騎着兔子背後，兔子還會躺在另一隻兔的頸上來顯示牠是較高層次(show dominance), 此行為停了就代表已決定了等級制度:<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/d9WUGogDlg4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fd9WUGogDlg4&d=CSzjam5d59%2B0TSQi2Kgm6kwFe44qEnauMGuWilFD6Zg%3D&h=b26c7eb5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/d9WUGogDlg4</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">資訊來源:&nbsp;<a href=\"http://rabbitspeak.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Frabbitspeak.com&d=CSzjam5d59%2B0TSQi2Kgm6kwFe44qEnauMGuWilFD6Zg%3D&h=0e12b20d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://rabbitspeak.com</a>&nbsp;(頭3個chapters)</span>"},{"pid":"b7f2039e652bbce4bb81c44a0fe1e1bf0dc1d4b1","tid":1788401,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T07:46:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\">Happy Holidays! Wishing you a new year full of peace and joy!</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}